-- Beijing Automotive Exploring Listing of BAIC Motor Unit, Company VP Says
-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 2010-10-11T04:26:21Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-11/beijing-automotive-exploring-listing-of-baic-motor-unit-company-vp-says.html
Beijing Automotive Industry Holding
Co. is considering selling shares of its unit BAIC Motor Co. in
an initial public offering, the company’s vice president Han
Yonggui, said in an interview today.  The company hasn’t decided on the timing of the IPO or the
amount it plans to raise, and it will use the proceeds to expand
its joint venture businesses and self-owned brands, he said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Bloomberg News at 
 swong139@bloomberg.net  